receyXP9Ww1fcSftM","ref":"Ezek.28.1","text":"The word of the LORD came again unto me, saying,","year":-588},{"id":"recFAdvsDvLJLME2r","ref":"Ezek.28.2","text":"Son of man, say unto the prince of Tyrus, Thus saith the Lord GOD; Because thine heart is lifted up, and thou hast said, I am a God, I sit in the seat of God, in the midst of the seas; yet thou art a man, and not God, though thou set thine heart as the heart of God:","year":-588},{"id":"recZx1JuAnsd8OJT1","ref":"Ezek.28.3","text":"Behold, thou art wiser than Daniel; there is no secret that they can hide from thee:","year":-588},{"id":"recqAmEpkByRbnE0m","ref":"Ezek.28.4","text":"With thy wisdom and with thine understanding thou hast gotten thee riches, and hast gotten gold and silver into thy treasures:","year":-588},{"id":"recfPUs2DH9YSKy6L","ref":"Ezek.28.5","text":"By thy great wisdom and by thy traffick hast thou increased thy riches, and thine heart is lifted up because of thy riches:","year":-588},{"id":"rec4wTKBkH04PIPQ8","ref":"Ezek.28.6","text":"Therefore thus saith the Lord GOD; Because thou hast set thine heart as the heart of God;","year":-588},{"id":"rec8eTBWYxaP1idlW","ref":"Ezek.28.7","text":"Behold, therefore I will bring strangers upon thee, the terrible of the nations: and they shall draw their swords against the beauty of thy wisdom, and they shall defile thy brightness.","year":-588},{"id":"recfrXrKdI341Ncu4","ref":"Ezek.28.8","text":"They shall bring thee down to the pit, and thou shalt die the deaths of them that are slain in the midst of the seas.","year":-588}]}
